---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const title = "Olimpiade degli Artisti | Talenti Creativi ed Eccellenze";
const description = "Una piattaforma curatoriale per valorizzare opere creative, talenti ed eccellenze.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <!-- Hero Premium -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[90vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden bg-deepviolet-950">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <img 
        src="/olimpiadeartisti-preview/hero_purple.svg" 
        alt="Institutional Backdrop" 
        class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-60"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 hero-overlay"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 text-center mt-[-10vh]">
      <div class="inline-block mb-6 animate-fade-in">
        <span class="block text-gold-400 font-serif text-lg md:text-xl tracking-[0.5em] uppercase mb-2">Le</span>
        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-9xl font-serif font-bold text-white tracking-tight mb-4 drop-shadow-2xl">
          OLIMPIADI <br class="hidden md:block"> DEGLI ARTISTI
        </h1>
        <div class="w-32 h-1 bg-gold-500 mx-auto"></div>
      </div>
      
      <p class="text-xl md:text-3xl font-serif text-violet-100 mb-12 tracking-wide max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Talenti Creativi ed Eccellenze <br>
        <span class="text-lg md:text-xl font-sans font-light uppercase tracking-[0.3em] block mt-4 text-gold-300">
          Premio <span class="at-symbol">@</span> OSC<span class="at-symbol">@</span>R <span class="at-symbol">@</span> Artisti ‚Äì Referendum Online
        </span>
      </p>
      
      <div class="glass-card p-8 md:p-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto rounded-none border-t-4 border-gold-500 shadow-2xl bg-deepviolet-900/40 backdrop-blur-xl border-white/10">
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white leading-relaxed font-light italic">
          "Un progetto culturale internazionale ispirato ai Giochi Olimpici
          dell'antica Grecia, fondato sui valori della Pace, della Bellezza e
          della Volont√† Popolare."
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Manifesto Section -->
  <section class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-white relative">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/3 h-full bg-violet-50/50 -z-10"></div>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
        <div class="relative">
          <img 
            src="/olimpiadeartisti-preview/peace.svg" 
            alt="Pace e Cultura" 
            class="shadow-2xl rounded-sm border-8 border-violet-100/50"
          />
          <div class="absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 w-48 h-48 bg-violet-200/30 -z-10 hidden lg:block"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <span class="text-violet-600 font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm">üåç Il Manifesto</span>
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-deepviolet-900 uppercase">
              Progetto Culturale<br>Internazionale
            </h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Ispirato ai Giochi Olimpici dell'antica Grecia, questo progetto nasce per celebrare 
            l'eccellenza artistica attraverso i valori universali della <strong>Pace</strong>, 
            della <strong>Bellezza</strong> e della <strong>Volont√† Popolare</strong>.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Una piattaforma dove talenti creativi possono emergere, essere riconosciuti 
            e valorizzati dalla comunit√† internazionale attraverso un sistema democratico 
            di valutazione e referendum online.
          </p>
          <a 
            href="/olimpiadeartisti-preview/progetto" 
            class="inline-flex items-center text-violet-600 font-semibold hover:text-violet-800 transition-colors group"
          >
            Scopri il Manifesto Completo
            <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Vision Section -->
  <section class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-50 to-gold-50/30">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
        <div class="space-y-8 order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <span class="text-gold-600 font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm">‚ú® La Visione</span>
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-deepviolet-900 uppercase">
              Arte, Cultura<br>& Democrazia
            </h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Creiamo un ecosistema dove l'arte incontra la tecnologia, dove la tradizione 
            si fonde con l'innovazione, e dove ogni cittadino pu√≤ partecipare attivamente 
            alla valorizzazione del patrimonio culturale contemporaneo.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="bg-white/80 p-6 rounded-lg border border-violet-100">
              <h3 class="font-serif font-bold text-deepviolet-900 mb-2">üé® 15 Categorie</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Pittura, Scultura, Fotografia, Design e molte altre discipline artistiche</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white/80 p-6 rounded-lg border border-violet-100">
              <h3 class="font-serif font-bold text-deepviolet-900 mb-2">üåê Referendum Online</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Votazione democratica aperta a tutti per scegliere le eccellenze</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative order-1 lg:order-2">
          <img 
            src="/olimpiadeartisti-preview/vision_purple.svg" 
            alt="Visione Artistica" 
            class="shadow-2xl rounded-sm border-8 border-gold-100/50"
          />
          <div class="absolute -top-10 -left-10 w-48 h-48 bg-gold-200/30 -z-10 hidden lg:block"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Categorie Premium -->
  <section class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-deepviolet-950 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
      <img src="/olimpiadeartisti-preview/greece_purple.svg" alt="Background" class="w-full h-full object-cover"/>
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="text-gold-400 font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm">üèõÔ∏è Le Discipline</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-white mt-4 mb-6 uppercase">
          15 Categorie Artistiche
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-violet-200 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Ogni forma d'arte ha il suo spazio, ogni talento la sua opportunit√† di brillare
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-5 gap-4">
        {[
          "üé® Pittura", "üóø Scultura", "üì∏ Fotografia", "‚úèÔ∏è Design", "üñºÔ∏è Illustrazione",
          "üé≠ Grafica", "üè∫ Ceramica", "üßµ Tessile", "üé¨ Video", "üèóÔ∏è Installazione",
          "üé™ Performance", "üìö Arte Digitale", "üéµ Arte Sonora", "üåø Land Art", "üíé Gioielleria"
        ].map((cat) => {
          const [emoji, ...nameParts] = cat.split(' ');
          const name = nameParts.join(' ');
          return (
            <div class="group bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm p-6 rounded-lg text-center hover:bg-white/20 transition-all duration-300 border border-white/20 hover:border-gold-400/50">
              <div class="text-3xl mb-3 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">{emoji}</div>
              <p class="font-semibold text-white text-sm uppercase tracking-wide">{name}</p>
            </div>
          );
        })}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Premium -->
  <section class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-gradient-to-r from-violet-600 to-gold-600 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/20"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-6 uppercase tracking-tight">
        Sei un Artista?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-violet-100 mb-12 leading-relaxed">
        Unisciti alla comunit√† internazionale di talenti creativi.<br>
        <span class="text-gold-200 font-light">La tua arte merita di essere riconosciuta.</span>
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center items-center">
        <a 
          href="/olimpiadeartisti-preview/artisti" 
          class="group bg-white text-violet-600 px-10 py-4 rounded-none font-bold uppercase tracking-wide hover:bg-gold-100 transition-all duration-300 shadow-2xl border-2 border-transparent hover:border-gold-400"
        >
          <span class="flex items-center">
            Esplora le Eccellenze
            <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6"></path>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>
        
        <a 
          href="/olimpiadeartisti-preview/contatti" 
          class="group bg-transparent border-2 border-white text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-none font-bold uppercase tracking-wide hover:bg-white hover:text-violet-600 transition-all duration-300"
        >
          <span class="flex items-center">
            Candidati Ora
            <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6v6m0 0v6m0-6h6m-6 0H6"></path>
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .animate-fade-in {
    animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-out;
  }
  
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
  
  .hero-overlay {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, 
      rgba(88, 28, 135, 0.8) 0%, 
      rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.6) 50%, 
      rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.4) 100%
    );
  }
  
  .glass-card {
    backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
  }
  
  .at-symbol {
    color: #f59e0b;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
</style>
